BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 128.64 610 Td (Why Toddlers Have Tantrums) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 575 Td (1. Big Emotions, Small Toolbox) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 559 Td (Toddlers feel emotions just as intensely as adults - anger, joy,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 543 Td (frustration, fear - but they have almost NO tools to manage them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 527 Td (They haven't learned words for feelings, deep breathing, or) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 511 Td (walking away. A tantrum IS their only tool right now.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 479 Td (2. Communication Frustration) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 463 Td (Your toddler knows what they want but often cannot express it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 447 Td (Imagine being in a foreign country where nobody understands you -) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 431 Td (that frustration is what your toddler feels daily. Limited) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 415 Td (vocabulary + big needs = explosive behavior.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 383 Td (3. Independence vs. Capability Gap) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 367 Td (Toddlers desperately want to do things themselves \(pour milk,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 351 Td (put on shoes, climb high\) but their motor skills and cognitive) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 335 Td (abilities haven't caught up to their desires. This gap between) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 319 Td ('I want to' and 'I can't yet' creates intense frustration.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 287 Td (4. Sensory Overload) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 271 Td (Toddler nervous systems are still developing. Loud noises,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 255 Td (bright lights, crowds, new textures, or too many transitions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 239 Td (can overwhelm their system. When overwhelmed, they shut down) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 223 Td (or explode - this is a protective nervous system response,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 207 Td (not misbehavior.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 175 Td (Remember:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 159 Td (Behind every challenging behavior is an unmet need or an) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 143 Td (underdeveloped skill. Our job is to figure out which one) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 127 Td (and help - not punish.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
