BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 97.44 610 Td (Emotion Coaching Scripts \(Page 3 of 5\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
q 0.85 g 50 575 332 18 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 55 580 Td (Scenario: Food Refusal) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 50 558 Td (What they're feeling: Asserting autonomy, sensory sensitivity, not hungry) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 542 Td (What to SAY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 529 Td ("You don't have to eat it. Your tummy will tell you when it's hungry.") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 513 Td (What NOT to say:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 500 Td ("You're not leaving this table until you finish!") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 484 Td (What to DO:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 471 Td (Offer food without pressure. Let them explore. No short-order cooking.) Tj ET
q 0.85 g 50 436 332 18 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 55 441 Td (Scenario: Separation Anxiety) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 50 419 Td (What they're feeling: Fear, insecurity, developmental phase) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 403 Td (What to SAY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 390 Td ("You're scared I'm leaving. I always come back. Let's do our special goodbye.") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 374 Td (What NOT to say:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 361 Td ("Just stop crying, I'll be right back! \(while sneaking out\)") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 345 Td (What to DO:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (Create a goodbye ritual. Never sneak away. Keep goodbyes short and confident.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
