BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 97.44 610 Td (Emotion Coaching Scripts \(Page 5 of 5\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
q 0.85 g 50 575 332 18 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 55 580 Td (Scenario: Whining) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 50 558 Td (What they're feeling: Unmet need, wants connection, tired, doesn't know how to ask) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 542 Td (What to SAY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 529 Td ("I want to help you. Can you use your regular voice to tell me?") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 513 Td (What NOT to say:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 500 Td ("I can't hear you when you whine! Stop that voice!") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 484 Td (What to DO:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 471 Td (Model the tone you want. Don't shame. Meet the underlying need.) Tj ET
q 0.85 g 50 436 332 18 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 55 441 Td (Scenario: Defiance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 50 419 Td (What they're feeling: Asserting independence, testing boundaries, power struggle) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 403 Td (What to SAY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 390 Td ("You don't want to put your shoes on. I hear you. We need shoes outside. Red ones or blue ones?") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 374 Td (What NOT to say:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 361 Td ("Because I said so! Do it now or else!") Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 50 345 Td (What to DO:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (Offer choices within boundaries. Make it playful. Avoid power struggles.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
