BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 108.48 610 Td (Gentle Boundary Setting Language) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 580 Td (How to Say No With Empathy:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 560 Td (Boundaries are not mean. They are how children learn safety,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 545 Td (structure, and what to expect. Deliver them with warmth and firmness.) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 520 Td (Instead of: 'No!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 506 Td (Try: 'I won't let you do that. Here's what you CAN do...') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 486 Td (Instead of: 'Stop it!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 472 Td (Try: 'I'm going to help you stop. Your body is telling me you need help.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 452 Td (Instead of: 'Because I said so') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 438 Td (Try: 'The rule is ___ because it keeps you safe.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 418 Td (Instead of: 'You're being bad') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 404 Td (Try: 'You're having a hard time. I'm here to help.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 384 Td (Instead of: 'If you don't stop...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 370 Td (Try: 'When you're ready, we can ___.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 350 Td (Instead of: 'Go to your room!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 336 Td (Try: 'Let's go to our calm-down spot together.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 316 Td (Instead of: 'I'm going to count to 3') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 302 Td (Try: 'I can see you need more time. I'll wait with you.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 282 Td (Instead of: 'Big kids don't cry') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 268 Td (Try: 'It's okay to cry. I'll be right here.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 248 Td (Instead of: 'You're fine') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 234 Td (Try: 'That was scary/hard. Tell me about it.') Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F1 9 Tf 50 214 Td (Instead of: 'Share NOW') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 9 Tf 60 200 Td (Try: 'When you're all done, it will be their turn.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 170 Td (Remember: Firm does not mean harsh. Kind does not mean permissive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 154 Td (You can hold a boundary AND hold your child's emotions at the same time.) Tj ET

endstream
