BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 88.32000000000001 610 Td (Self-Regulation Development Milestones) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 580 Td (What to Expect at Each Age \(Every child is different!\)) Tj ET
q 0.88 g 50 552 332 16 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 55 555 Td (Age 1 \(12-18 months\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 535 Td (* Beginning to understand 'no' \(but cannot consistently follow it\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 522 Td (* Tantrums begin as communication develops) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 509 Td (* Easily distracted/redirected) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 496 Td (* Separation anxiety peaks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 483 Td (* Cannot share or take turns yet) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 470 Td (* Needs immediate comfort when distressed) Tj ET
q 0.88 g 50 444 332 16 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 55 447 Td (Age 2 \(18-30 months\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 427 Td (* 'NO!' becomes a favorite word \(healthy autonomy!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 414 Td (* Tantrums peak in frequency and intensity) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 401 Td (* Beginning to name some emotions with help) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 388 Td (* Parallel play \(playing beside, not with, peers\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 375 Td (* Can follow simple 1-step directions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 362 Td (* Needs co-regulation for all big emotions) Tj ET
q 0.88 g 50 336 332 16 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 55 339 Td (Age 3 \(30-42 months\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 319 Td (* Can start to use words for some feelings) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 306 Td (* Beginning to wait short periods) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 293 Td (* Starting cooperative play) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 280 Td (* Can follow 2-step directions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 267 Td (* May use simple calming strategies with prompting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 254 Td (* Tantrums decrease slightly but may get more intense) Tj ET
q 0.88 g 50 228 332 16 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 55 231 Td (Age 4 \(42-54 months\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 211 Td (* Can identify basic emotions in self and others) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 198 Td (* Beginning to problem-solve simple conflicts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 185 Td (* Can wait longer \(with support\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 172 Td (* Starting to internalize some regulation strategies) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 159 Td (* Can follow rules in structured settings) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 60 146 Td (* Still needs help with big emotions regularly) Tj ET

endstream
